params.812: Reach level 20 in the Magic skill.
params.813: Ensure you have runes for a spell you can cast at your Magic level. The Frogs in the swamp south of Lumbridge are suitable targets to fight.
params.814: Ensure you have a spell set that you can use and have the runes for.|The Frogs in the swamp south of Lumbridge are suitable targets to fight.|Giant Frogs drop big bones which grant more Prayer experience than regular bones.
params.823: Bring food when using Magic as the Magic armour leaves you vulnerable to melee.
